# Go bindings (gen/go) ARE committed: Go consumers vendor them read-only at the
# proto tag via `go.mod` (CONTRACTS.md §4), so the tagged tree must carry them.
# Regenerate with `make gen` (buf generate) — never hand-edit. Python bindings
# stay out of git; Python consumers regenerate (`make gen`) or pin the dist.
/gen/python/

